00:47:14.932 --> 00:47:18.266
<i>Local pastor, David
Hill, is basically staging</i>

00:47:18.369 --> 00:47:21.237
<i>his very own version of what
can only be described here</i>

00:47:21.339 --> 00:47:23.501
<i>as a Senate filibuster.</i>

00:47:23.607 --> 00:47:25.367
<i>His last-ditch effort
to delay the demolition</i>

00:47:25.443 --> 00:47:26.536
<i>of his church.</i>

00:47:26.844 --> 00:47:28.073
"When it came to pass..."

00:47:28.179 --> 00:47:29.859
<i>As you can see here,
he's literally reading</i>

00:47:29.947 --> 00:47:32.348
<i>the Bible cover to cover
while the growing crowds</i>

