I have a signed injunction
from Judge Pascual that says...

00:47:43.160 --> 00:47:44.992
Well, you can read it yourself.

00:47:45.096 --> 00:47:47.395
"Cease and desist."

00:47:50.368 --> 00:47:52.030
Good?

00:47:52.136 --> 00:47:54.105
- Thank you.
- Let's go!

00:47:59.443 --> 00:48:01.121
All right, guys, we're done.

00:48:01.145 --> 00:48:03.080
Time to leave. Let's go.

00:48:03.180 --> 00:48:04.273
What happened?

00:48:04.382 --> 00:48:06.112
I just bought us three weeks.

00:48:06.217 --> 00:48:07.879
Thank you.

00:48:07.985 --> 00:48:09.296
<i>So, maybe the university's</i>

00:48:09.320 --> 00:48:11.084
board of trustees
does have the right

00:48:11.188 --> 00:48:12.918
to expropriate the
church property.

00:48:13.023 --> 00:48:14.651
But even if it's
legal, is it moral?

